window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When I received the notice my divorce was final, I decided the best way to celebrate my freedom was to have one night of passion with a complete stranger. No strings attached.</b></p> <p>I chose the hottest club in town, Rapture, to find my prey. Little did I know the person I hooked was the head of the Irish Mafia, who became haunted by the memory of our night.</p> <p>When I drunkenly return to Rapture with a broken heart, I find myself being drawn into the dark underground world of the Irish Mafia and the four men that rule it.</p> <p>As my normal, perfectly managed life slowly unravels, these men help me to reconnect with the woman I once was, and she wasn't always innocent. Will I be able to rebuild a life I truly desire, or is it all just an illusion?</p> <p><i>These Sinful Delights</i> is a why-choose dark mafia romance set in the fictional world of Sinners Bay. This is the first book in a series of interconnected standalones set in the same world.</p>"; 
